The paper deals with revenue management problems, which involve decision-making under uncertainty. This is a topic that falls under game theory (cs.GT), machine learning (cs.MA), and optimization (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of linear programming relaxations and adaptation of optimal stopping theory, which are topics in data science (cs.DS) and information theory (cs.IT).
